{"tid":2092304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚悚！台灣男子活吞蝙蝠　大讚：甘甜美味","createTime":"2020-07-03T07:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T05:40:26.000Z","uid":209657,"like":17,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"558703caafef99d6d345a5c72b2a896083544410","tid":2092304,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎尚未結束，網路上竟然有民眾PO出活吞蝙蝠當下酒菜的畫面！這是一名工人抓到年幼的蝙蝠，將蝙蝠捏在手中展示，然後再將蝙蝠放到嘴巴裡咀嚼活吞，最後還配一口啤酒，這大啖活蝙蝠的畫面被PO到爆料公社，讓網友看得都直呼「太誇張！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/none/c82b377c3fbb97c9a91a8808fa88e5b4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200703/_2020070312050093107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2Fc82b377c3fbb97c9a91a8808fa88e5b4%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200703%2F_2020070312050093107.jpg&h=81e409b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8efa993eaf37edf7984e95d67829b66f507b849","tid":2092304,"uid":307927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"蝙蝠俠"},{"pid":"6b18ac4f4bce1e6074d60d0a51cda302cb336318","tid":2092304,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:03:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=771971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D771971&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=c6c7c1ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D771971&h=4ecda531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=771971</a><br />\n這段影片是1名身穿綠色上衣的工人，帶著草帽在烈日下捕捉到1隻年幼蝙蝠，一手捏著蝙蝠，另一隻手還拿著鐵鎚，然後還向鏡頭展示確認蝙蝠是活的，還用客語說：「有看到嗎？蝙蝠！」一旁的友人說：「現抓現吃、甘甜美麗。」並在旁發出笑聲。綠色工人手中捏著的年幼蝙蝠，被捏到嘴巴張得大開，下一步驚悚畫面出現了！工人竟然直接將蝙蝠塞進口中開始咀嚼，<span style=\"color: red;\">蝙蝠因被咬痛到雙腳不斷抽搐</span>。最後工人整隻放進嘴裡咬，還配了一口啤酒，再張開嘴巴展示「真的活吞吃光光！」最後用台語大讚：「甘甜美麗。」"},{"pid":"c79a2bc852a0040303c165ff5ceb09c8b2f6b408","tid":2092304,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uc-ouOgt_D8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fuc-ouOgt_D8&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=c4c5bbb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uc-ouOgt_D8</a>"},{"pid":"3d5677196b9787fa409e15bdce492e845277dd5a","tid":2092304,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"雞肉味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c02411e406b93fa1fa7b0e57e9c021cdff8ce5","tid":2092304,"uid":189109,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"中武肺死啦仆街冚家剷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd51351522fdb9b15baf22f970ee6a69815d1794","tid":2092304,"uid":28504,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"厚格過av喎老細...."},{"pid":"1bb96d27560eb2e03d419dec218a27334a21848a","tid":2092304,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fd51351522fdb9b15baf22f970ee6a69815d1794","tid":2092304,"uid":28504,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"厚格過av喎老細...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/02/phpGNTJax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F02%2FphpGNTJax.jpg&h=83b954c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"111867d0f38875c2115a54bb8c2259578382a42e","tid":2092304,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm